If you’re looking for a magical place to walk off into the sunset, this boardwalk in Gros Morne National Park is where your dreams can come true! Whether you’re looking for a dreamy, romantic sunset, or an invigorating outdoor adventure, a trip to Gros Morne is exactly what you’re looking for!
